item.description: And finally, after a few days of frequent troubleshooting, I have been able to launch my new website! Some additional math: \[ \max_x \text{ } \sum_{i=1}^N w_i x_i \] \[ \sum_{i=1}^N w_i = 1\] \[ f(x) = \frac{\pi}{6} - \sin(2 \pi)\]
